| 1Ô∏è‚É£ | Intended Workflow           | What is the normal journey? What steps must happen in order? Where do money, credit, limits, or permissions change? | Map flow step-by-step                                       | `Step 1 ‚Üí Step 2 ‚Üí Step 3 ‚Üí Completion`                   |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Identify where steps can be skipped, repeated, or reordered | Logic bugs live here                                      |
| 2Ô∏è‚É£ | Skip Steps                  | Can later steps be accessed directly?                                                                               | Call Step 3 without Step 1                                  | `POST /checkout/complete`                                 |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Call Step 2 twice                                           | Without `POST /checkout/pay`                              |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Complete without confirmation                               | Missing validation                                        |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Finalize without validation                                 | Broken flow enforcement                                   |
| 3Ô∏è‚É£ | Repeat Actions (Replay)     | Are one-time actions actually one-time?                                                                             | Re-submit same request                                      | Replay attacks                                            |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Reuse tokens, IDs, references                               |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Repeat after success                                        |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     |                                                             | Wins: double refunds, duplicate credits, multiple coupons |
| 4Ô∏è‚É£ | State Assumptions           | Does the server blindly trust state?                                                                                | Change `status` manually                                    |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Modify `completed=true`                                     |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Set impossible states                                       |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Mix states across users                                     |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     |                                                             | `{ "status":"approved","paid":true }` without paying      |
| 5Ô∏è‚É£ | Critical Value Tampering    | Are client values trusted?                                                                                          | Modify price, quantity                                      |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Modify discount, currency                                   |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Modify limits, IDs                                          |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     |                                                             | Try: negative, zero, large, decimals                      |
| 6Ô∏è‚É£ | Authorization in Logic      | Can valid access still be abused?                                                                                   | Act on other users‚Äô objects                                 |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Act outside role scope                                      |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Change ownership mid-flow                                   |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     |                                                             | `POST /orders/{id}/cancel` (not yours)                    |
| 7Ô∏è‚É£ | Method & Endpoint Confusion | Are all methods and APIs protected?                                                                                 | Change HTTP method                                          |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Try alternate endpoints                                     |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Test mobile/internal APIs                                   |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     |                                                             | `GET ‚Üí 403`, `PUT/DELETE ‚Üí 200`                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     |                                                             | `/api/mobile/`, `/api/v2/`, `/api/internal/`              |
| 8Ô∏è‚É£ | Time & Sequence Abuse       | Are time rules enforced?                                                                                            | Use expired tokens                                          |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Submit after timeout                                        |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Act before allowed time                                     |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Act after cancellation                                      |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     |                                                             | Cancel after delivery, refund after chargeback            |
| 9Ô∏è‚É£ | Feature Chaining            | Can features interact unexpectedly?                                                                                 | Feature A affects Feature B                                 |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Cross workflows                                             |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Mix user roles                                              |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     |                                                             | `Create ‚Üí Transfer ‚Üí Cancel`, invite ‚Üí remove ‚Üí retain    |
| üîü  | ‚ÄúShouldn‚Äôt Happen‚Äù          | What would the business never allow?                                                                                | Free money                                                  |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Unlimited resources                                         |                                                           |
|     |                             |                                                                                                                     | Acting on others‚Äô behalf                                    |                                                           |
